 |date        = 2006-10-19
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927201445/http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3154522
 |archivedate = 2007-09-27
}}
</ref>。DICE則回應該程式只會回報玩家所看的廣告和時間長度<ref>{{cite web
 |url       = http://www.totalbf2142.com/forums/showthread.php?p=66802#post66802
 |title       = 廣告的不利傳言
 |author       = "CKMC"
 |publisher       = Total Battielfield 2142
 |access-date       = 2008-07-09
 |archive-date       = 2008-05-02
 |archive-url       = https://web.archive.org/web/20080502000519/http://www.totalbf2142.com/forums/showthread.php?p=66802#post66802
 |dead-url       = yes
 }}</ref>。[[澳洲|澳洲]]玩家在該程式执行時沒有可變廣告組件<ref>
{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.kotaku.com/gaming/wtf-mate/wtf-mate--aussie-bf2142-lacks-spyware-note-208326.php
 |title       = 搞什麼，朋友? 澳洲玩家沒有間諜軟件警告
